window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The Montgomerys are heading north to Boulder, Colorado. These Montgomerys hold their secrets close and their family closer…at least that’s what they’ve told themselves over the years. When their world shifts on its axis, however, each sibling will have to fight for a way to find their equilibrium, as well as who they thought they were before everything changed. Breaking down their own barriers won’t be easy, but they’re Montgomerys and never back down from a challenge—even when the challenges happen to be the ones they never saw coming.</p> <p><i>Includes </i><b><i>Wrapped in Ink</i></b><i> and </i><b><i>Sated in Ink</i></b><i>.</i></p>"; 
